# GitHub Personal Access Token — increases API rate limit from 60 → 5000 req/hr
# and unlocks accurate repo/star/follower counts.
# HOW TO CREATE: https://github.com/settings/tokens/new
#   → Token name: cv-portfolio-readonly
#   → Expiration: No expiration (or 1 year)
#   → Scopes: public_repo (read-only is enough)
# NOTE: SSH key fingerprints (SHA256:...) are for Git SSH auth only — they
# CANNOT be used here. You need a classic or fine-grained PAT from the URL above.
VITE_GITHUB_TOKEN=

